EnExplanation: The state of being free from noise or disturbance; a lack of sound.

Samples.EeSentence: Palun ole vaikust, ma tahan lugeda.
Samples.EnSentence: Please be quiet, I want to read.

Samples.EeSentence: Ma tahan veidi vaikust, et lugeda raamatut.
Samples.EnSentence: I want a little silence to read a book.
